CustomField.description: Rounding values will be decimal numbers. 0.01 to round to the nearest cent; 0.5 to round to the nearest 50 cents; 1 to round to the nearest dollar, 10 to round to the nearest ten dollars, etc. If the value is null, no rounding will be applied.
